subject: Olympic Games (2008)
Track and Field
lead_paragraph: American sprinter Lolo Jones lost in the 100-meter hurdles, while her teammate, Dawn Harper, grabbed the gold. Also Usain Bolt advanced toward Wednesday’s historic 200-meter race.
